Glossary

SBE

Simple Binary Encoding optimized for low latency of encoding and decoding.

FIXP

FIX Performance Session Layer based on SBE.

FIXP Connection

It is comprised of four or three iterations: negotiate (is not required for intra-day connections), establish, message exchange, and terminate.

FIXP Session

It is comprised of one or more FIXP connections, meaning that a FIXP Session spans multiple establishments.
